    <div class="container">
                    <div class="left">
                <article class="editor"><h3 class="homepage-title title"><span style="color: #00926b; font-size: 46px;"><strong>Inspiring Minds, </strong></span></h3>
<h3 class="homepage-title title"><span style="color: #00926b; font-size: 46px;"><strong>Nurturing Hearts, </strong></span></h3>
<h3 class="homepage-title title"><span style="color: #00926b; font-size: 46px;"><strong>Enriching Tomorrow</strong></span></h3></article>
            </div>
                            <div class="right">
                <article class="editor"><ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Builds strong foundations for learning within a joyful, creative and challenging environment.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Develops a holistic learning community that cares for and protects all members.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Inspires and empowers responsible citizens to take action on a personal, local and global level.<br /></span></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="rounded_title bg-colour1"><span style="color: #ffffff;"><a style="color: #ffffff;" href="https://bradbury.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/what_we_stand_for/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discover Our Vision</a></span></p></article>
            </div>
                            <div class="responsive">
                <article class="editor"><h3 class="homepage-title title"><span style="color: #00926b; font-size: 46px;"><strong>Inspiring Minds, </strong></span></h3>
<h3 class="homepage-title title"><span style="color: #00926b; font-size: 46px;"><strong>Nurturing Hearts, </strong></span></h3>
<h3 class="homepage-title title"><span style="color: #00926b; font-size: 46px;"><strong>Enriching Tomorrow</strong></span></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Builds strong foundations for learning within a joyful, creative and challenging environment.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Develops a holistic learning community that cares for and protects all members.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Inspires and empowers responsible citizens to take action on a personal, local and global level.<br /></span></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="rounded_title bg-colour1"><span style="color: #ffffff;"><a style="color: #ffffff;" href="https://bradbury.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/what_we_stand_for/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discover Our Vision</a></span></p></article>
            </div>
            </div>
</section>
<section id="section2">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What can Bradbury School offer your family?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper bg-colour2">
        <div class="container">
            <ul>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/41f6d723321637028224ef42cb90b25b.png" alt="ESF_Logomark_BW_RGB" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">ESF Network</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>As part of the English Schools Foundation(ESF), our students are supported by the largest English-medium international school organisation in Hong Kong, providing them the resources and opportunities not found outside of ESF Schools.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://bradbury.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/marketing_family/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/b743f6e2a0308848d14af7faff91f1f5.png" alt="World-class Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Innovative Teaching Methods</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our child-centred approach harnesses the IB PYP to foster critical thinking, creativity, and 21st-century skills.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://bradbury.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/9b9fd04d2bd030ad988d63452f41337f.png" alt="Strong School-Family Connection" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Strong School-Family Connection</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We partner with you to understand your child's unique needs and tailor our teaching accordingly.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://bradbury.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/parent_partnership/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/b3c35a1196499917a49946cf2b05e12b.png" alt="Well-rounded Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Well-rounded Education</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our world-class facilities, from gymnasiums to performing arts spaces, ensure a diverse learning experience.</p>
