                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>Technology in The Shed</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>Bradbury actively engages students, equipping them with future-ready skills. The Shed, our maker space, fosters coding, design, and engineering through hands-on projects across the curriculum, developing essential 21st-century competencies.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://bradbury.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/specialist_provision/">
