                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>Performing Arts at Bradbury School</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>Our school's performing arts program lets students explore music, dance, and drama, integrating with the curriculum and offering extracurricular activities for collaboration, confidence, and creativity.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://bradbury.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/extra_curricular_activities/">
                                    <span>Find out more</span>
                                </a>
