            <div class="lightbox" data-id="449">
            <div class="lightbox-wrapper">
                <button class="close"></button>
                <div class="lightbox-container">
                    <time>25/03/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>On Monday, 23rd March, Year 1 held a Writing Celebration of Learning. It was great to welcome parents into the classroom and see each child confidently share their writing. Students demonstrated clear improvements in handwriting, more accurate spelling, and the use of adjectives. They also enjoyed playing a phonemic game, highlighting their growing reading and decoding skills. We appreciate you taking the time to celebrate your child’s achievements and to support their learning this term.</h3>
