                    <time>24/03/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>The wider Bradbury community (Y1 to 5 parents) are invited to pop in and check out the Year 6 PYP Exhibition which will be happening on Wednesday and Thursday between 10.50am and 12.00 noon in the Hall. We'd love to see you!</h3>
