                    <time>24/03/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>🎉 Huge congratulations to Jeremy P. in Year 3 for achieving his Red Belt in Taekwondo on Sunday!  We’re so proud of his hard work and dedication! Keep it up, Jeremy!</h3>
