                <div class="lightbox-container">
                    <time>23/03/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>Today we are congratulating Javen Hooi for showing diligence and hard work. This weekend he took part in his taekwondo exam and graduated to a Black Belt! We are really proud of him, he was very nervous last week and we spoke a good deal about how with self belief and positivity ‘you can do hard things!’ And he absolutely can!</h3>
