                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>Joey from Year 3 is sharing her artwork. On the left, "Snowflakes" ❄️ on the right, "Flowers" 🌸. <br><br>Joey drew a lot of inspiration from @the_oblivious_mind’s colourful geometric style. Drop a ❄️ for Snowflakes or a 🌸 for Flowers — tell us why!</h3>
