                    <time>20/03/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>We are incredibly proud of our Year 2 students for sharing their “Sharing the Planet” learning with their parents this morning. The students presented fact books, art dioramas, virtual coded worlds and play provocations. It was a wonderful morning and we thank all the parents who joined us for our Celebration of Learning. 🐆🦓🐒🐠🦋</h3>
